# 🤖 AI-Powered Code Reviewer and Quality Assistant

An intelligent code review system that leverages AI to analyze source code, detect issues, and provide actionable suggestions for improving code quality, readability, and performance.

---

## 🚀 Features

* 🔍 Automated code analysis
* 🐞 Bug detection and issue identification
* 💡 AI-based code improvement suggestions
* 📊 Code quality evaluation
* ⚡ Fast and efficient processing
* 🌐 Supports multiple programming languages *(if applicable)*

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### 👨‍💻 Languages

* Python
* JavaScript *(if frontend is included)*

### ⚙️ Frameworks & Libraries

* Flask / FastAPI *(backend framework – update accordingly)*
* React.js *(if frontend exists)*
* OpenAI API / LLM integration *(or any AI model used)*
* NumPy / Pandas *(if used for processing)*

### 🔧 Tools & Platforms

* Git & GitHub (Version Control)
* VS Code (Development Environment)
* Postman (API Testing)
* Docker *(if used)*

---

## 📦 Dependencies

Make sure you have the following installed:

* Python 3.x
* pip (Python package manager)

### Install required packages:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

